==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Argentic
<hw>Ar*gen"tic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, derived from, or containing, silver; -- said of
certain compounds of silver in which this metal has its lowest
proportion; <as>as, <ex>argentic</ex> chloride</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Argentiferous</ent>⟦br⟧
